title: Coney Island–Stillwell Avenue station
summary: Coney Island–Stillwell Avenue (also known as Coney Island Terminal and signed on some trains as either Coney Island or Stillwell Avenue) is a New York City Subway terminal in Coney Island, Brooklyn. It is the railroad-south terminus for the F, N, and Q trains at all times and for the <F> train during rush hours in the peak direction.
